{"tid":407763,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生日好少人記得，灰到極點","createTime":"2017-09-20T16:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T20:05:30.000Z","uid":133865,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e37c8d1cad2a1873be0b9de4bfd90a1702fde8","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"話說小弟前兩日生日<br />\n唔好話咩生日飯，就連句生日快樂都係得三個人同我講，係，你冇睇錯，係得三個人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好同我講咩fb生日提示，唔中意fb，所以已經冇用好多年<br />\n<br />\n之前喺外國讀書既時候有班fd，可能同一屋簷下大家close啲，所以夜晚都會出去食餐飯，飲下酒咁<br />\n<br />\n點知返到黎香港讀大學，連句生日快樂都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔知係真係唔記得吖，定講都費事講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩都仲叫做有屋企人肯理下我，是但同我慶祝下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我唔洗真係落街買個嘉頓自己慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，唔知點形容，總之真係灰到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d98957f6869f20a98cee60a9c1623d7e56ebc1","tid":407763,"uid":41737,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbb63b3d4a9c2407eb3571bc28d203eda8d613e9","tid":407763,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:28:04.000Z","msg":"生日快樂 補返"},{"pid":"a97cf7a66afe22dee192283658b1a257dc42386c","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日快樂 補返</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33145133098ce3dd281354e1097620f4ba14f14","tid":407763,"uid":132898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"樓主唔洗咁灰，到你大大下就會發覺就算有一個人記得你生日已經值得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2180f7796845b34d017e2d1bce9a8c6cd2b19db6","tid":407763,"uid":109768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:32:25.000Z","msg":"唔係玩得埋既fd都唔會刻意去記生日啦<br />\n仲要冇fb提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有三個咪算係咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同事都唔知我生日幾時啦<br />\n雖然我都唔知佢地幾時生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b7f22a2c6155a759b9033daf139a590b33e1ec","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個已經好多架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我真係好多謝佢地喺冇咩fb提示下都仲記得，不過...唉算，至少都總算知道自己喺人地心中有幾唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7dcd6c4d62ed653504a3585b82743de051d7a5","tid":407763,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"Btw生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1514fcc456a20a5047f70e0f681ffa33a5a4a4","tid":407763,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d072422d14e8716d7444fd2b4188929ac111a80e","tid":407763,"uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"過多幾年就慣，i know that feel bro<br />\nBTW, 補返句祝福比ching，生日快樂！"},{"pid":"1d3a88828c9bdb97f4d8fe10887a2205afaa314a","tid":407763,"uid":62064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"除左屋企人之外 廿歲生日無人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c094641cb37287d17f23b01887a73ddabb3f4c5","tid":407763,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"其實有時就算好friend 都未必記得住個生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbb495ac5f3ad940cf03f260b74bc1833de34c6","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多幾年就慣，i know that feel bro<br />\nBTW, 補返句祝福比ching，生日快樂！</blockquote><br />\n希望大學會識到班fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過如果冇既就希望可以慢慢習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aff6690026a0a39ac3b38fe78b3ee3bc64f1599","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有時就算好friend 都未必記得住個生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我見其他人自己有gp fd既都會互相慶祝大家生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6253f2fb8c5d0df70e7c7490a2201b2ccd3b5a2c","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"推多下等多啲人陪我訴下苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f2bf31503f3f60fa58eda41d85a2edd78322d6","tid":407763,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"冇提示都仲有三個，樓主好幸福架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed463717830badb69982d19111dab39c7a0194a8","tid":407763,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:51:16.000Z","msg":"曾經有個人話會記得。。"},{"pid":"1c8147958e37ea81e146667180bb04946095aece","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經有個人話會記得。。</blockquote><br />\n前度...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4367b9d03dfae5f850de8242856971e5956caa","tid":407763,"uid":133865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0